<item>
            <title>[LU-16763] Improve Lustre kunit testing and OBD life cycle testing</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-16763</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Lustre has a number of small kernel modules used to run various unit tests. It would be useful to consolidate and standardize these. Additionally:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;I saw some issues with sanity/60a in: &lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/c/fs/lustre-release/+/50583&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/c/fs/lustre-release/+/50583&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Improving and debugging run-llog.sh&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Improvements to OBD life cycle testing.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
</description>
